{"body": "Rails 4 has been announced for the summer. How much PATCH support should we get in? There have been various proposals of how to support PATCH in Rails 4:\r\n\r\n* make PATCH and PUT both map to `update` and:\r\n  * make edit forms use PATCH by default and PUT by configuration opt-in\r\n  * make edit forms use PUT by default and PATCH by configuration opt-in\r\n* split `update` into different actions that map better to PUT and PATCH", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3224949", "created_at": "2011-12-20T20:42:11Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/505#issuecomment-3224949", "updated_at": "2011-12-20T20:42:11Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 505, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/dlee", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/139de3f8c3d6ee008cdb3abd3da23908?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F80177fe965b78111f4dfee80cfdc3689.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/received_events", "gravatar_id": "139de3f8c3d6ee008cdb3abd3da23908", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "dlee", "type": "User", "id": 7035, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dlee/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52385f14bd3543c151012166"}, "id": 3224949, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/505"}
